  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC444">
        <l>ītā koṭuveṉak kiḷakku mūṉṟu</l>
	<l>miraviṉ kiḷavi yākiṭa ṉuṭaiya.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/246/mode/1up">246</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/246/mode/1up">246</ref>.</p>
<p>iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, ituvum kiḷavi yākkattuk kūṟappaṭātu oḻintuniṉṟatōr marapilakkaṇam uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>urai : ik kūṟappaṭṭa mūṉṟum irappōr collutaṟkuriya eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>oruvarai yoruvar irakkuṅkāl im mūṉṟaṉuḷ oṉṟucolli yirappatu eṉṟavāṟu.	(48)</p>
 </body>
  </text>

